data.description: Back on the market through no fault of the seller - This 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom house features a large open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a spacious living room, and a gorgeous keeping room with a fireplace. The home has 3 fireplaces that can be enjoyed throughout the house in different settings. The oversized master bedroom has a sitting room and fireplace, while the huge secondary bedrooms have walk-in closets and are quite spacious. Recent upgrades include new light fixtures and ceiling fans, new hardwood floors on the first level, upgraded roof (2018), a new gas stove, and more! The enclosed patio at the back is an ideal spot for relaxing or entertaining any time of year along with a backyard that is perfect for kids and pets. The home features a 3 car garage with more than enough space for parking and storage. The subdivision features a pool and tennis courts.
